ogle&#8217;s best practices, and the realities of marketing in Kenya.<\/div><\/div>[vc_tta_accordion][vc_tta_section title=&#8221;How is local SEO different from regular SEO?&#8221; tab_id=&#8221;1715360052221-d2dccac3-2f8e82d6-a9a5&#8243;][vc_column_text css=&#8221;&#8221;]<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"344\" data-end=\"576\">Local SEO focuses specifically on improving your visibility in a defined geographic area. It helps your business appear in localised search results on Google \u2014 especially in the \u201clocal pack\u201d (the top 3 map listings) and Google Maps.<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"578\" data-end=\"679\">While traditional SEO aims to rank your site nationally or globally, local SEO targets searches like:<\/p>\n<ul data-start=\"680\" data-end=\"743\">\n<li data-start=\"680\" data-end=\"707\">\n<p data-start=\"682\" data-end=\"707\">\u201crestaurant in Westlands\u201d<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"708\" data-end=\"726\">\n<p data-start=\"710\" data-end=\"726\">\u201clawyer near me\u201d<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"727\" data-end=\"743\">\n<p data-start=\"729\" data-end=\"743\">\u201cspa in Ruiru\u201d<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p data-start=\"745\" data-end=\"962\">It involves optimising your Google Business Profile, location pages, reviews, schema, and local citations \u2014 areas that traditional SEO might overlook.<\/p>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title=&#8221;Can I do this for multiple business locations?&#8221; tab_id=&#8221;1715360052312-795bf34f-889a82d6-a9a5&#8243;][vc_column_text css=&#8221;&#8221;]<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"1020\" data-end=\"1170\">Yes. If your business operates in more than one town, city, or estate, we can create a structured local SEO strategy for each location. That includes:<\/p>\n<ul data-start=\"1172\" data-end=\"1380\">\n<li data-start=\"1172\" data-end=\"1268\">\n<p data-start=\"1174\" data-end=\"1268\">Setting up and optimising a separate Google Business Profile per branch (as allowed by Google)<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"1269\" data-end=\"1332\">\n<p data-start=\"1271\" data-end=\"1332\">Creating individual landing pages optimised for each location<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"1333\" data-end=\"1380\">\n<p data-start=\"1335\" data-end=\"1380\">Managing local reviews and listings by branch<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p data-start=\"1382\" data-end=\"1519\">This is essential for chains, franchises, and multi-location service businesses \u2014 and we handle it all as part of your local SEO package.<\/p>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title=&#8221;What if I already have a Google Business Profile?&#8221; tab_id=&#8221;1715361191995-ff8a0d69-1fe982d6-a9a5&#8243;][vc_column_text css=&#8221;&#8221;]<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"1580\" data-end=\"1680\">If your profile is already set up, we audit it for completeness, accuracy, and performance. We then:<\/p>\n<ul data-start=\"1682\" data-end=\"1867\">\n<li data-start=\"1682\" data-end=\"1752\">\n<p data-start=\"1684\" data-end=\"1752\">Optimise your categories, services, images, and business description<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"1753\" data-end=\"1799\">\n<p data-start=\"1755\" data-end=\"1799\">Add schema on your website to match GBP data<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"1800\" data-end=\"1867\">\n<p data-start=\"1802\" data-end=\"1867\">Monitor and improve your visibility for target keywords and areas<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p data-start=\"1869\" data-end=\"2033\">A well-maintained Google Business Profile can significantly increase calls, direction requests, and website visits \u2014 but it needs ongoing attention to perform well.<\/p>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title=&#8221;How long does it take to rank locally?&#8221; tab_id=&#8221;1715361240947-6ed290f2-a03582d6-a9a5&#8243;][vc_column_text css=&#8221;&#8221;]<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"2083\" data-end=\"2167\">Most local SEO improvements begin to show impact within 30 to 90 days, depending on:<\/p>\n<ul data-start=\"2169\" data-end=\"2313\">\n<li data-start=\"2169\" data-end=\"2213\">\n<p data-start=\"2171\" data-end=\"2213\">How competitive your area and industry are<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"2214\" data-end=\"2263\">\n<p data-start=\"2216\" data-end=\"2263\">How optimised your current profile and site are<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"2264\" data-end=\"2313\">\n<p data-start=\"2266\" data-end=\"2313\">The quality and quantity of reviews and content<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p data-start=\"2315\" data-end=\"2548\">For example, a cleaning company in Nairobi may start appearing in the local 3-pack within two months, while a legal firm in a more saturated area may take a bit longer. We provide monthly reports so you can see your progress clearly.<\/p>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title=&#8221;What if I work from home or don\u2019t want to show my address?&#8221; tab_id=&#8221;1715361291476-30b845c7-304f82d6-a9a5&#8243;][vc_column_text css=&#8221;&#8221;]<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"2618\" data-end=\"2733\">That\u2019s fine. Google allows you to hide your address and operate as a <strong data-start=\"2687\" data-end=\"2712\">service-area business<\/strong>. This is common for:<\/p>\n<ul data-start=\"2735\" data-end=\"2831\">\n<li data-start=\"2735\" data-end=\"2748\">\n<p data-start=\"2737\" data-end=\"2748\">Freelancers<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"2749\" data-end=\"2804\">\n<p data-start=\"2751\" data-end=\"2804\">Mobile service providers (e.g., electricians, tutors)<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"2805\" data-end=\"2831\">\n<p data-start=\"2807\" data-end=\"2831\">Home-based entrepreneurs<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p data-start=\"2833\" data-end=\"2970\">We\u2019ll help you configure your profile accordingly and optimise for the towns or areas you serve, rather than a physical walk-in location.<\/p>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_tta_section][\/vc_tta_accordion][\/vc_column][\/vc_row]<\/p>\n<\/div>","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>[vc_row equal_height=&#822